descriptionHTML:
YSAR fancy skull watch face collection is made for most stylish smartwatch users.To get our fashionable skull watch face means that you have modern style and exceptional taste. Features are simple(Time and ambient mode) as much attention was paid to modern and elegant design.

Our watch faces are available in settings right after you download from store and are simple in being set up. YSAR watch faces do not require much energy, so your smartwatch will operate for almost the same period of time as usual.


Watch Faces by YSAR design are absolute symbols of style. Watch faces by YSAR Design are compatible with both round and square android wear smartwatches: Moto 360, Asus ZenWatch, LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, LG Watch Urbane, Samsung Gear Live, Sony Smartwatch 3 etc..

Check out our watch faces with different features and designs: https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=YSAR+Design

Please, rate, share and write comments, because we want to improve our watch faces and satisfy your needs.
